data.enText: a date that is an exact number of years after the date of an important or special event

data.chText: 在他妻子去世的周年忌日
data.enText: on the anniversary of his wife's death

simple_means.memory_skill: anni〔= ann〕年，一年 + vers 转 + ary 物 → 一年转到一次 → 周年纪念

tr: the date on which an event occurred in some previous year (or the celebration of it)

value.def: An anniversary is a date which is remembered or celebrated because a special event happened on that date in a previous year.

example.ex: ...the one hundredth anniversary of the birth of Ho Chi Minh.
example.tran: 胡志明诞辰一百周年纪念

trans: 快乐周年；纪念日快乐；结婚周年快乐；周年快乐；周年纪念快乐
